organic.title: National Domestic Violence Hotline: Domestic Violence Support
organic.snippet: Everyone deserves relationships free from domestic violence. When you're ready, we're here to listen with confidential support 24/7/365.

organic.title: A New Leaf | Ending Homelessness, Domestic Violence, & More
organic.snippet: A New Leaf helps families and individuals overcome homelessness, domestic violence, and more. We believe in helping families, changing lives.

organic.title: Access Dozens Of Community Programs - Contact A New Leaf
organic.snippet: If you are experiencing homelessness call Centralized Services at 877-211-8661. Families should call The Family Housing Hub at 602-595-8700.
